Package: packmp3
Version: 3.0a
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Yade Bravo <https://github.com/YadeWira/packMP3>
Installed-Size: 6464
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: libc6, libstdc++6, zlib1g, liblzma5
Description: Lossless MPEG audio compressor (MP3/MP2/MP1)
 packMP3 losslessly recompresses MP3 (Layer III), MP2 (Layer II) and
 MP1 (Layer I) audio files, reconstructing the exact original file bit
 for bit. Embedded ID3v2 JPEG/PNG cover art is recompressed too, via
 the sibling packJPG and packPNG libraries.
